<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.11">
<l>poruḷeṉṟiv vulakam paṭaittavaṉ pukaḻmēṉ</l>
<l>maruḷil vaṇkurukūr vaṇcaṭa kōpaṉ</l>
<l>teruḷkoḷḷac coṉṉa vōrāyirat tuḷippat</l>
<l>taruḷuṭai yavaṉṟā ḷaṇaivikku muṭittē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This decade among the one thousand spoken clearly</l>
<l>by generous Caṭakōpaṉ from unconfused, liberal Kurukūr</l>
<l>on the praise of him who created this world as matter</l>
<l>finally brings one close to the feet of him who possesses grace.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
